headline.print_headline: White House Says No Issue With Biden's Son, Ukraine Gas Company
headline.main: White House Says No Issue With Biden's Son, Ukraine Gas Company

lead_paragraph: The White House on Tuesday brushed aside questions about whether the involvement of Vice President Joe Biden's son in a Ukrainian natural gas company raised ethical issues at a time when the administration is promoting energy diversity in the country.
